data.description: **SAVE $$$ BY ASSUMING EXISTING FHA LOAN at 2.80%** MAJOR PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!  Welcome home! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath BEAUTY features your very own SPARKING POOL, NEWER ROOF, BRAND NEW STAINLESS STEEL APPLICANCES & VIVINT SECURITY SYSTEM complete with video doorbell, rear camera & coded front door lock!! Step inside and you'll be greeted by an open and airy floor plan featuring vaulted ceilings, tile floors, arched walkways and spacious rooms throughout. The generously sized living room is highlighted by tall ceilings and a chalkboard wall the family will adore. The sun drenched dining space is perfect for hosting, complete with sliding glass doors leading to the lanai and pool for those unforgettable gatherings with family & friends. Prepare your favorite recipes in the BEAUTIFUL kitchen with stainless steel appliances, bar top seating, light grey shaker cabinets with glass hardware, and convenient access to the laundry room. Relax and recharge in the LARGE primary suite filled with natural light and tall ceilings. The primary bath offers ample counter space for getting ready, along with a soaking tub, walk in closet, private toilet/shower, and pool access. Three bright guest bedrooms with wood style floors provide comfort and serenity. The guest bathroom features a tub/shower combo with easy access to the guest bedrooms. Outside you'll find a STUNNING poolside oasis complete with a screened lanai, water view of the nearby pond, and the EASY TO MAINTAIN POOL with a tranquil waterfall feature.  Nestled between Lake Apopka and Wekiva Springs, this home offers quick access to main roads including 441 and 429—a short drive to shopping and dining - including downtown Mt. Dora, Wekiva Springs, Altamonte Springs and more!! Spend the weekends kayaking, camping, fishing, and enjoying the wondrous nature nearby. You’ll also be minutes away from nearby schools and other amazing finds that make this one of the most desirable areas in Central Florida! Don’t miss out on this amazing property in a EXCELLENT LOCATION – view the 3D virtual tour and call TODAY for a private tour while the competition is sleeping!!
